        "那曹操他对人假模假样"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（中军、刘表同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘表",
          "line_type": "引子",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "荆襄八郡地，文武一身尊。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘表",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "某，荆州牧刘表。昨日曹丞相有书到来，将祢衡推荐与我，我想祢正平乃天下\n知名之士，那曹孟德平日礼贤下士，何以弃而不用，推荐前来，其中必有缘故。\n我不免将夫人请出，再做计较。\n中军，有请夫人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "中军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。有请夫人。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（中军下。蔡夫人上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡夫人",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "忽听主公唤，移步到堂前。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（蔡夫人进门。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妾身有礼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘表",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫人少礼。请坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢座。主公将妾身唤出，有何话讲？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘表",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫人，是你有所不知，昨日接到曹丞相一信，荐来祢衡。那祢正平乃天下名士。\n那曹孟德何以弃而不用，反来推荐与我？"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你也太糊涂了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘表",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我怎么糊涂呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听妾身道来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "那祢衡生来禀性狂，\n怎能够与曹操共处一堂。\n因此上才将他转荐外方。\n这便是借你刀来把他伤。"
        },
        {
          "character": "那曹操他对人假模假样、倘若是主公你不加容量、刘表",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来如此。那曹操他杀了祢衡，怕天下人耻笑，难道我就不怕么。夫人，你看\n此事如何处置才好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "若依妾身主张，\n不如荐他到外厢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘表",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "荐到哪里？"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "江夏黄祖，生性鲁莽，且将他荐到那里，再看如何。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘表",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫人高见，正合孤意。夫人请回，我依计而行。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（蔡夫人下。中军上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "中军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启禀主公：祢衡求见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘表",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吩咐升帐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "中军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "升帐。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘表",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "祢衡进见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "中军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "祢衡进见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来也。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（内西皮导板） 听中军传一声命我进见，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（祢衡上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "刘景升果然是不能尊贤。\n且把那国家事讲在当前。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（祢衡进见。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "明公在上，祢衡拜见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘表",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "少礼，请坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢座。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘表",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正平，你由朝中到来，朝中之事如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "明公容禀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "那曹瞒在朝中大权独揽，\n眼见得汉家业被他推翻。\n怕只怕荆洲地也难苟安。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公本是天潢派岂可不管、刘表",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "公本是天潢派岂可不管、刘表",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "那祢衡当孤面对我责难，\n生就了狂妄性名不虚传。\n我把他荐黄祖这有何难。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公本是天潢派岂可不管、刘表",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正平，孤家这里，地僻事少，不足以容高贤之驾。意欲将你荐于黄祖帐下，你\n可愿去？"
        },
        {
          "character": "倘若是杀了他曹操笑俺、祢衡",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "倘若是杀了他曹操笑俺、祢衡",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "那曹贼定下了借刀之计，\n刘景升虽昏庸岂能不知？\n也不过转借刀将我命追。\n破出去一身死有何稀奇。"
        },
        {
          "character": "倘若是杀了他曹操笑俺、祢衡",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "明公既然荐俺，岂有不去之理。就此告辞了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "他把我荐黄祖哪有好意、我若是不敢去惹他耻笑、刘表",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "去吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "辞别了刘景升忙跨坐骑，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（祢衡上马。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我见了黄祖再看高低。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（祢衡下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘表",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "只见祢正平扬长去了，"
        }
      ],
